.SH ENVIRONMENT
.IP RUST_LOG
Tracing/log filter (tracing\-subscriber EnvFilter syntax, e.g. "rift_wm=debug" or "info,rift_wm::actor=trace").
.IP RUST_BACKTRACE
Standard Rust backtrace control. rift forces this to "1" if unset.
.IP RIFT_BS_NAME
Mach bootstrap name used for the rift IPC server. Override only when running multiple rift instances side\-by\-side.
.IP RIFT_EVENT_TYPE
Set on subscriber commands: event name ("workspace_changed", "windows_changed", "window_title_changed", "stacks_changed").
.IP RIFT_WORKSPACE_ID
Set on subscriber commands: workspace identifier for the event.
.IP RIFT_WORKSPACE_NAME
Set on subscriber commands: workspace name for the event.
.IP RIFT_WORKSPACE_INDEX
Set on subscriber commands: workspace index (when available).
.IP RIFT_WINDOW_COUNT
Set on subscriber commands for windows_changed events.
.IP RIFT_WINDOWS
Set on subscriber commands: comma\-separated list of window ids.
.IP RIFT_WINDOW_TITLE
Set on subscriber commands for window_title_changed events.
.IP RIFT_PREVIOUS_WINDOW_TITLE
Previous title before a window_title_changed event.
.IP RIFT_EVENT_JSON
Full JSON payload of the event being delivered.
.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.SH FILES
.IP ~/.config/rift/config.toml
User configuration file.
.IP ~/.rift/
Runtime data directory.
.IP ~/.rift/layout.ron
Layout restore file (legacy).
.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
